summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over portions of Lots 1, 2, 24, and 25 in Block 10 of the Palisades Addition; over portions of Lots 11 and 12 in Block 5 of Lake Washington Shore Lands Section 2 and a portion of 55th Avenue Northeast as vacated by Ordinance 47372 for ingress and egress to maintain an existing Sanitary Sewer.
